The paper focuses on the development of explainable AI for robotic teammates, which involves human-robot interaction and decision-making. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). The paper also discusses the use of AI and robotics, which suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics) as likely categories. The paper also mentions the mental workload of humans in highly demanding tasks, which could fall under cs.CY (Computational Complexity) or cs.SY (Systems and Control).
